label: Annual Reports of the Chief of the Fire Department of the City of Charleston
description: A set of annual reports of the the Fire Department from 1859-1872. Reports missing for  years 1862-1865. The annual reports open with a statement from the Fire Chief and include multiple lists of department expenses, financial cost of fires, the cause of the fires, and locations of city property pertaining to the fire department.
